A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Video Lottery Operations – Campaign Contributions – Parity Act
3 FOR the purpose of repealing the prohibition on applicants for and holders of video lottery
4 operation licenses and persons who own an interest in video lottery facility
5 operations in the State from directly or indirectly making contributions to certain
6 campaign finance entities; and generally relating to campaign finance contributions
7 by persons with an interest in video lottery operations.
